text: ovun mata dan̆ḍuvama patita vū kalhi ahō mūsā ! obagē paramādhipati oba vetin pratignā gat ayurin oba apa venuven ohugen prārthanā karanu mænava ! mema dan̆ḍuvama apa vetin oba ivat kara dunnē nam niyata vaśayenma api oba va viśvāsa karannemu. tavada oba saman̆ga isrāīl daruvan va yavannemu yæyi ovuhu pævasuvōya
